			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If you already know how to play EQ, I suggest you go to PC at level 13ish - that should last you through level 20ish. At level 22 or so, you should be able to fear-kite gnolls in SK, or go to Overthere, out the east (?) side gate, then move to the Skyfire ramp area. You can stay in OT for another 10-15 levels 'til you ding 35ish. 
<br />

<br />
Do you have LDON? If not, I would suggest buying it - IMO it's worth it. 2nd or 3rd best expansion IMO.
<br />

<br />

<br />
EDIT: So in other words, wait until you're about level 20ist to start kiting, IMO. OT is a great zone, as is SK to fear/aggro kite. If you do not want to wait, I suggest learning it in BBm with wandering greenbloods (they'll be blue to you) or in Steamfont at the Mino slaver camp (blue also) or even in Western Karana with spiders and such.
<br />

<br />
Just my 2cp worth.<br />_________________<br />Xerbilix Xilibrex
<br />
Gnome Defiler
<br />
Sol Ro
