				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I just started fear kiting in OT, on the East side at lvl 16.  Mobs are blue to red being level 15 - 20ish over there.
<br />

<br />
I use about 20% of mana per kill, given one snare and about 3 fears.  Not too bad really.  Haven't had too much of a problem sticking spells on them, and you are free to kill anything over there.  Some hit harder than others, but you aren't getting hit right? =)
<br />

<br />
Najor</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
